vote.title: Authorize a one-year service price agreement between the Pacify Health, LLC and City of Dallas to continue providing statewide nonfee assistance service for City residents with access to twenty-four-hour on demand lactation support through the Office of Community Care and Empowerment for a term of one year from September 1, 2025 through August 31, 2026 - Pacify Health, LLC, sole source - Not to exceed $400,000.00 - Financing: - FY26 Texas Lactation Support After-Hours Hotline Funds
